name: Distressed_Reclaimed-look_Black_Dining_Table
reviews: Table is heavy and true to picture. Realize that legs assemble with 2 screws into table only. Thus weight is not supported by the legs underneath which hopefully will not be a problem. Not real wood but a composite overlay.
The table is beautiful, great quality and adds elegance to a room
description:
Create a warm and and inviting dining area with this distressed reclaimed-look dining table. This table can sit up to six people, and can be paired with matching side chairs or a bench for a more casual look. The black square post legs adds just the right amount of contrast to complete the rustic look of this dining table.

Includes: One (1) dining tableMaterials: MDF, pine woodFinish: Black distressed finishDimensions: 30 inches high x 38 inches wide x 64 inches longStyleContemporaryMaterialMDF, WoodFinishBlack Finish, DistressedShapeRectangleAssemblyAssembly Required
